Description: Functions that generate planar and spherical triangle meshes,
    computes finite element calculations for 1- and 2-dimensional flat and curved
    manifolds with associated basis function spaces, functions for lines and
    polygons, and transparent handling of coordinate reference systems and
    coordinate transformation, including 'sf' and 'sp' geometries. The core
    'fmesher' library code was originally part of the 'INLA' package, and also
    distributed in the EUSTACE Horizon 2020 project.
